name: Bitco-gain
body:
### Welcome to Bitco Gain Home page.
This is page of the project Bitco Gain you can find more about it here.

### How it works
You can think of Bitcoins as Dollars except that it you won't find a printed one any where :smile: Similar to the Dollars who's value changes based on the demand. So our apps helps you gain money by buying Bitcoins at the lower price and sell them at a higher price when the demand is high.

### Authors and Contributors
Tummala Dhanvi (@dhanvi) Atla Ravinder Reddy (@ravinderatla)
